---
// components/MethodologySteps.astro
---

<section
    class="relative w-full bg-black py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden"
>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2
                class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase tracking-tighter"
            >
                EL PROCESO
            </h2>
            <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#aba070] mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div
                class="group relative p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-4 hover:bg-white/10"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-6 right-8 text-5xl font-black text-[#aba070]/10 group-hover:text-[#aba070]/20 transition-colors uppercase italic"
                >
                    01
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-xl font-black text-white mt-8 mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase"
                >
                    EVALUACIÓN INICIAL
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
                    Analizamos tu punto de partida: composición corporal,
                    historial de entrenamiento, objetivos y estilo de vida.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <div
                class="group relative p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-4 hover:bg-white/10"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-6 right-8 text-5xl font-black text-[#aba070]/10 group-hover:text-[#aba070]/20 transition-colors uppercase italic"
                >
                    02
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-xl font-black text-white mt-8 mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase"
                >
                    DISEÑO PERSONAL
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
                    Creo un plan de entrenamiento y nutrición adaptado a ti. Sin
                    plantillas, solo estrategias para tu contexto.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3 -->
            <div
                class="group relative p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-4 hover:bg-white/10"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-6 right-8 text-5xl font-black text-[#aba070]/10 group-hover:text-[#aba070]/20 transition-colors uppercase italic"
                >
                    03
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-xl font-black text-white mt-8 mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase"
                >
                    SEGUIMIENTO
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
                    Entrenas con propósito mientras monitoreo tu progreso.
                    Ajustamos el plan según tus resultados.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 4 -->
            <div
                class="group relative p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-4 hover:bg-white/10"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-6 right-8 text-5xl font-black text-[#aba070]/10 group-hover:text-[#aba070]/20 transition-colors uppercase italic"
                >
                    04
                </div>
                <h3
                    class="text-xl font-black text-white mt-8 mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase"
                >
                    RESULTADOS
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">
                    No solo alcanzas tus metas, aprendes a mantenerlas. Te
                    enseño a entender tu cuerpo para siempre.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Decorative blur -->
    <div
        class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-[#aba070]/5 blur-[150px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"
    >
    </div>
</section>

